Codes for the Blinkenwall

So far in this repository:

- blink
General library to send data to the wall, and utility to read
RGB data from stdin and transmit to the wall.

- blinkenwall_show
a tiny programm to simulate the blinkenwall, require stdin data in ppm rgb

-tetris
tetris for the blinkenwall with stdout

-snake
snake for the blinkenwall with stdout


see also: https://metalab.at/wiki/Blinkenwall.com
